
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-vanrein-httpauth-sasl-04.txt'>
    <title>"HTTP Authentication with SASL", Rick van Rein</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-vanrein-httpauth-sasl-04.txt</link>
    <description>Most application-level protocols standardise their authentication exchanges under the SASL framework.  HTTP has taken another course, and often ends up replicating the work to allow individual mechanisms.  This specification adopts full SASL authentication into HTTP.</description>
    <dc:date>2020-03-04T08:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
